<body>

    <section class="top_bar">
    <a href=""><img src="/icons/groups.png" alt=""></a>
    <a href=""><img src="/icons/help.png" alt=""></a>
    <a href=""><img src="/icons/profile.png" alt=""></a>
    <a href=""><img src="/icons/logout.png" alt=""></a>
    </section>

    <div class="info_text">  <p> <span class="orange_highlight">Search Or View  </span> groups you can join.</p></div>
  
    <div class="space_between" id="search_button_frame">
        <button>Search</button>
        <button>View All</button>
        <p></p>
    </div>

    <p class="body_text"> <span class="orange_highlight">Created </span> is groups you’ve created, here you can manage the groups you made or view them.</p>
     
    <p class="body_text"> <span class="orange_highlight">Joined </span>  is groups you’ve joined, you can choose which one you want to view right now.</p>

    <p class="body_text"> <span class="orange_highlight">Create </span> is where you go to create a group, enter a name, description and you can do a password if you want it to be private otherwise with no password it will be public.</p>

 
  

    <div class="space_between" id="create_button_frame">
        <button>Created</button>
        <button>Joined</button>
        <button>Create</button>
        
    </div>
      


    <form id="create_group_form">
        <span class="orange_highlight">Create Group</span>
      
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Name">
  

       
        <input type="text" id="password" name="password"  placeholder="Password">
    

      
        <input id="text" name="description" placeholder="Description " >
        

        <button type="button">Create Group</button>
    </form>

    <br>

    
     

